description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results of the Dow Jones U.S. Financial Services Index composed of U.S. equities in the financial services sector.
 The fund generally invests at least 90% of its assets in securities of the underlying index and in depositary receipts representing securities of the underlying index. The underlying index measures the performance of the financial services sector of the U.S. equity market. The fund is non-diversified.
